{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_08_end","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_08_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-8","storyName":"她的影子","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"战胜自己内心深处的恐惧后，苇草成功控制源石技艺治疗了同伴。当爱布拉娜发出战争的号召时，苇草也对同伴们说出了自己的理想。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_08_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_08","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":15,"next":17,"characters":["爱布拉娜","苇草","莫兰","塔拉流民","维多利亚军官","深池军官","受伤的塔拉人"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"她想象过一切结束的可能，哪怕德拉克的火永远无法平息。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"她想象着盛怒的烈焰从她灼痛的胸口迸发，焚毁她被赋予的外壳与身份，令她从此挣脱自己的枷锁。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"但当她真的去触摸自己的火焰，想要将其握住的时候，她突然在想，会不会自己从来都没有控制过它。","id":11},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":13},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"character","id":15},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_bg_34_g8_galekingruins_inside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":19},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0.7","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"做得好，拉芙希妮。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你想要我真心地夸赞你，这就够了吗？","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"还是说，你已经准备好了......影子要寻回自己，你想要取代我成为“领袖”？","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我可以给你这个机会。你的下一簇火就能将我烧成灰烬。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_npc_722_1#4$1","afrom":"0","ato":"0.8","duration":"0","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你要......向我伸出手吗？","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"charslot","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"火焰燃烧着，她的影子微微摇动。","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"但苇草移开了视线。","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"不远处刚刚醒来的凯莉在垫着的旧围裙上慢慢地撑起身体，莫兰哼着歌帮她清洗伤口。","id":34},{"type":"dialog","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......姐姐，你为什么会来这里？","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"站在这里的时候，你看到的是什么？","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":39},{"type":"charslot","id":40},{"type":"text","text":"那天夜里的篝火很明亮。","id":41},{"type":"text","text":"那时，维恩正走来走去祈求新的落脚地好做生意，塞尔蒙给自己的武器缠上更多铁丝。","id":42},{"type":"text","text":"大家开着玩笑叫她领袖，又认真地说，多谢她把大家领到这里。","id":43},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我听说，维多利亚人为盖尔王授衔，然后才在仪式石阵的上方建起了王城。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在那以前......它先是塔拉人栖居的家园。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":48},{"type":"charslot","id":49},{"type":"text","text":"她想起很早以前的节日冬夜。","id":50},{"type":"text","text":"她们在壁炉前换上一模一样的新外套，留下了一张两人都微笑着的照片。","id":51},{"type":"text","text":"那是令人喜爱的......一小团温暖的火。","id":52},{"type":"dialog","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"middle","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"所以......不。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"自己是影子，这件事，我不在乎。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但我不是你的影子。我只是，人们理想中“领袖”的影子。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"他们想要一条逃生的路，想找回自己的生活，而我恰好在那里，被他们所需要。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"姐姐，我为什么要战胜你呢？","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":61},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":63},{"type":"character","id":64},{"type":"charslot","id":65},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_bg_34_g8_galekingruins_inside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":67},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":68,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":70},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"不怕死？请别这么说，凯莉，怕死也不是一件坏事。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我们还没有帮到其他塔拉人，就死在同样想救塔拉人的深池手里，多遗憾。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"......你啊，比以前，能说会道多了。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"multiline","name":"塔拉流民","text":"还好，我们还有消炎药......","id":76},{"type":"shake","name":"left","power":"5","times":"2","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"multiline","name":"塔拉流民","text":"嘶......","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"弄疼你了？抱歉......","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"啊，苇草，你回来了。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":84},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":85},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我们今晚躲在这里的话，应该不会再遇到那些被源石技艺控制的死者。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"你去检查附近的情况了？那就好。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#4$1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我也希望能多停留一段时间，凯莉的伤......情况很差。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"怎么，你的表情......","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"......呵呵，我还记得，一开始，我们把你当成医生，后来才知道，我们所有人，都只是负伤的人。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"我的伤，很严重？","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不，不是那样......你的伤是可以痊愈的，不用这么担心。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......只是，你们害怕我的火吗？","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"当然不会。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":108},{"type":"text","text":"于是她向眼前受伤的塔拉人伸出手。","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"德拉克的怒火在她的血液中翻涌。昔日红龙替他的子民流血，一滴血便烧毁整片原野。","id":110},{"type":"text","text":"她咽下炙热的吐息，被抑制的火灼烧着她。","id":111},{"type":"text","text":"但如果，这样能抚平伤痛，她愿意忍受。","id":112},{"type":"dialog","id":113},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_field_healfield_loop","volume":"0.6","channel":"heal","loop":"false","id":114},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":115},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"heal","volume":"0","fadetime":"2","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"——她的手中并未真的燃起火焰，甚至没有任何光芒闪过。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"只是所有人都产生了一种感觉——生命在流淌，轻柔得像清晨里的第一次睁眼。","id":118},{"type":"dialog","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"呼......","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"看你的表情......感觉好受一些了？","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"是啊......你啊，苇草，难道你真的是医生？但是医生也不是像你这样办事的呀。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":127},{"type":"multiline","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":129},{"type":"multiline","name":"苇草","end":"true","text":"不，只是，这终于是我自己的火焰了。","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"愿你今晚能睡个好觉，凯莉。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"4","id":134},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":136},{"type":"character","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"5","id":138},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_bg_34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":140},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$stranger_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_bat_stranger_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":141,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"我从未想过，维多利亚军队之外的人，也能登上这艘高速战舰。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"深池军官","text":"我以为在它降下维多利亚旗帜的时候，你们就该想到这一点。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_406_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"我对你没有敌意，塔拉人，我只是对你们的军事素养，还有你们那位领袖感到好奇。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"我不希望公爵难得的客人，只是倚仗了自己的德拉克血统。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"深池军官","text":"你的骨子里充满对我们的傲慢，维多利亚人。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_406_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"深池军官","text":"可等她登上台开始演讲，你会发现，她才是这艘战舰上所有势力的主人。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_406_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":156},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormflp","channel":"wind","volume":"0.4","loop":"true","id":159},{"type":"character","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","id":161},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_34_g2_reedmarshes.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","y":"50","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":163},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_reedmarshes","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"reed","id":164},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的塔拉人","text":"我还是不明白，你们到底是不是深池？毕竟，你们穿得不太像深池的人。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_729_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的塔拉人","text":"当然，不管你们是什么人，你们从维多利亚人手里救了我的命，我想跟着你们一起走。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_729_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......抱歉，我们没有帮到你的同伴。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的塔拉人","text":"没事......没事。我要是能去救其他人，就算是把他那份活回来了。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_729_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......好。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"说起来，苇草，那些人是不是已经放弃追捕我们了？","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，追踪的队伍消失得有些突兀，但无论如何，对我们来说是好事。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":179},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.1","fadetime":"2","id":180},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"深池的军队，应该已经集结完毕。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......塔拉人即将向整个维多利亚，发出自己的声音。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"wind","id":189},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-100","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"10","block":"false","id":190},{"type":"zoom","name":"middle","xpos":"0.8","ypos":"0.8","scale":"1.5","fadetime":"10","block":"false","id":191},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"50","xTo":"-150","yTo":"-100","xScaleFrom":"1.3","yScaleFrom":"1.3","xScaleTo":"1.3","yScaleTo":"1.3","duration":"2","block":"false","id":192},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":193},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"background","id":195},{"type":"character","id":196},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"reed","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":198},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_bg_34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":199},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","volume":"0.7","id":201},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":202},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"wind","id":203},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"士兵们。","id":205},{"type":"dialog","id":206},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_34_i07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","id":207},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":208},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act22side/m_avg_act22side_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":209,"musicid":3},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我所带领的深池部队，从维多利亚各地来到这里，与公爵阁下的军队会合，是要共同打响一场事关生存的战争。","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"在今天之前，许多人或许还未听说过深池的名号，或者不理解我们究竟在为什么而战斗。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你们的战争此时蓄势待发，不过，我们的斗争却已经在过去十年里发生许多次了。即使是此时，也有代表塔拉人的部队正在流血。","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"塔拉人所遭受的，只用虐待一词来概括，恐怕已经不够。我看到他们的街道化为灰烬，他们的城市变为废土。","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"而所求不过饱腹的塔拉人顶着被处决的风险迎接我们的士兵，将他们的面包掰给我们一半。","id":214},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#4$1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我看到塔拉人在挣扎着向我们呼救。不过，他们不是苦苦等待了十年，而是等待了数百年。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他们恳求自己有力的同胞......也恳求有良知的邻人，恳求那些不愿与残暴者为伍的维多利亚人。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他们恳求我们的正视。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"此刻，我们中的一些人知道自己是塔拉人，而另一些人或许会问，我们究竟将要向谁施以援手？","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":223},{"type":"character","id":224},{"type":"image","id":225},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":226},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_34_g2_reedmarshes.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":228},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":229},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"塔拉人，塔拉人。和你在一起待久了，我们都习惯用这个词了。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#3$1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"可我其实总是在想你说的话，苇草。你说我之前所在的工厂车间，缺少防护措施，所以大家都会慢慢感染矿石病，慢慢死掉。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"但是，将塔拉人撵去危险的地方工作的工厂老板，自己也是塔拉人。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"也有许多，像你这样说话完全是标准维多利亚口音的人。他们和我们出生在同一个地方，但最害怕和我们闲谈，暴露自己的乡音......","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"塔拉人到底是什么？我们要救什么人？","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......我也想了很久。你想听我的看法吗？","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"说吧，苇草，既然没那么急着逃命赶路，我们当然乐意听你说。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯......现在的我也许会说，它是几百年之后，我们身上的苦难终于得到的一个名字。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"过去，维多利亚人花了很多年，把塔拉这个名字抹掉了。可是，你们一定也感觉到过，自己是跟一些印象联系在一起的。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"维多利亚人不叫我们塔拉人，他们说“那些口音粗鄙、没有教养的乡巴佬，那些游手好闲的无赖，那些出身不正的下等人”......","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"reed","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"character","id":251},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_34_i07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"又或者，如许多人经历过的那样，他们依据我们的族姓，光明正大地从我们身上夺走更多的财产、封地与权利......甚至我们亲眷的性命。","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"也许会有人对我们说，那么为什么不放弃你们的语言与传统呢？为什么不在节日里同维多利亚人唱一样的歌谣呢？","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"只要人们看不出我们是塔拉人，我们就能与他们得到一样的对待。","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"当然，也会有人说，自己虽然是塔拉人，但也靠着意志与野心得到了财富，接受了足够的教育而跻身上流社会。","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——多么讽刺，我们必须告别自己的文化，背叛自己的家庭，才能从他们那里挣得被视作一个普通人的尊严。","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我们当中不乏卓有成就的英才，可成就的第一步却是把自己变成维多利亚人。","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"威灵顿公爵阁下，您一定比任何人都理解......","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"还有多少人记得您流淌着塔拉人的血呢？","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","name2":"avg_npc_241","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"......","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_241.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#4$1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"只是，既然维多利亚处心积虑地试图夺走我们的名字，那他们自己真的已经遗忘了塔拉的存在吗？","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"要真是那样，为什么塔拉王朝覆灭两百年后，我，盖尔王的后裔，一条幸存的德拉克。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——会看着我的父母被阿斯兰的刺客暗杀，倒在血泊之中？","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他们仍在害怕，怕我们想起自己的名字，从而戳穿他们的谎言。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"而我正是来让大家重新想起这一切的。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_722_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"character","id":278},{"type":"image","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":280},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_34_g2_reedmarshes.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":281},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"所以你是说，很多年前，维多利亚的贵族来到了塔拉，把所有塔拉人都变成了自己的领民？","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，史书里大致告诉了我们这些。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"关于塔拉的事，有许多是编造出来的，但也有真实的部分。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"维多利亚强行将塔拉地区的君主分封为盖尔王，胁迫他册封许多维多利亚贵族。对塔拉地区的不公待遇，也写在了明文条例中。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那个时候开始，塔拉人的口音就和他们的身份地位联系在了一起。维多利亚人指责塔拉人愚笨、粗鄙、缺乏教育。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"reed","id":293},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"character","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"但又有谁来教过塔拉人？这几百年来，从没有人教过我们。","id":297},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_34_i07.png","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","x":"100","screenadapt":"showall","id":299},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"100","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-100","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.3","yScaleFrom":"1.3","xScaleTo":"1.3","yScaleTo":"1.3","duration":"40","block":"false","id":300},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","grad":"true","id":301},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","grad":"true","id":302},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"塔拉人已经慢慢地从最初那片土地上逃出去了，也许随着移动城市漂流到了维多利亚各处，但却从未获得过与维多利亚人同等的选择权。","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"名门宴会与高等学府里，可曾有我们的位置？我们之中如果有许多游手好闲的人，难道不是因为维多利亚人夺走了我们工作的权利？","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"在“塔拉人”一词消失的漫长岁月里，我们所承受的不公就是这么巧妙地隐藏了自己，直到现在，我们终于发现自己被逼上绝路的原因。","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"1","fadetime":"3","id":309},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"1","fadetime":"3","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":311},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":312},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":313},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"character","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"无论是塔拉的历史，还是后人编出的、寻溯塔拉渊源的传说，我都知道很多。","id":316},{"type":"dialog","id":317},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_34_i08.png","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","x":"100","screenadapt":"showall","id":318},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-100","yFrom":"0","xTo":"100","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.3","yScaleFrom":"1.3","xScaleTo":"1.3","yScaleTo":"1.3","duration":"40","block":"false","id":319},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"1","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"2","grad":"true","id":320},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"1","fillto":"0.2","fadetime":"2","grad":"true","id":321},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"真实的不公，虚构的梦想，这些，我都可以讲给你们听。","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"可是，我不说这些，你们也会想......从过去的生活里逃出去。","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"那还用说，我们活不下去了嘛！","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，所以，就算我们认不出自己是塔拉人，也没关系。","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我只是想，熄火钟敲响的地方，每个人都需要烧穿黑夜的火。","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我们要对抗的，只是横加在我们身上的不幸。","id":329},{"type":"dialog","id":330},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","grad":"true","id":331},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.2","fillto":"0","fadetime":"3","grad":"true","id":332},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":333},{"type":"dialog","id":334},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":335},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":336},{"type":"character","id":337},{"type":"background","id":338},{"type":"image","id":339},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":340},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":343},{"type":"subtitle","text":"所以，我们不得不为了塔拉人的生存而战斗。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.12","width":"700","id":344},{"type":"subtitle","id":345},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":349},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":350},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"character","id":352},{"type":"background","id":353},{"type":"image","id":354},{"type":"largebg","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":356},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_34_i07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"眼下，我们正停靠在橡林郡，这里曾有塔拉人的街区，但在一些暴虐之徒燃起的大火中化为灰烬。","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"如果我们之中有视力足够优秀的人，或许能看见那边被天灾摧毁的塔拉王城。这些都是塔拉人身上的伤痕。","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"不过，我们的意图绝不在于找回旧日的塔拉土地，重建那些历史的残骸。","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我们是新的大地上的流浪者，我要带你们去走的，是建起一个新时代、一种新秩序的道路。","id":363},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_34_i09.png","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","x":"-50","fadetime":"3","id":365},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-50","xTo":"0","duration":"8","block":"false","id":366},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——这艘战舰的下一次停靠，将会在伦蒂尼姆的港口。","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"当然，我们不是为争夺维多利亚的冠冕而去。我们只是为了从维多利亚人那里换回我们的命运，将它握在自己手中。","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我们如今已经看得很清楚，这些不幸始于维多利亚对塔拉强加的统治与奴役，那么，我们该让维多利亚自己否认过去所作所为的正当性。","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"这场战争或许不会止于伦蒂尼姆，不过，我们难道会害怕一场漫长的苦战吗？","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"火已经燃起来了。","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"它将烧尽这片大地上陈旧的秩序，烧尽我们身上腐朽的枷锁。","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"而在将到来的新秩序里，我恳请你们所有人。","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我恳请你们不分塔拉与维多利亚，不分地域与出身，只为那光荣的公正而战斗，为前所未有的时代而战斗。","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"直到塔拉人与维多利亚人一样，得以自由地书写自己的梦想，谁也不能阻拦我们。","id":376},{"type":"dialog","id":377},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"character","id":380},{"type":"background","id":381},{"type":"image","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":383},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_34_i08.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":384},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"wind","id":385},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"reed","id":386},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"但是，苇草，我们要与什么战斗呢？“要让塔拉人活下去”，这种说法有点太模糊了。","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯......过去，我总是想，生命很脆弱。","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"在这片土地上，有很多东西等着杀死我们。我们所有的努力，只不过是拼命地与死亡搏斗、抗争。","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"当然，最后没有人能获胜。","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"如果太在乎人们的性命，我要怎么面对无处不在的牺牲，和无法追究的横死？","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"可是，生命的分量，就是很沉。我不能逃避它。","id":394},{"type":"dialog","id":395},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_34_i10.png","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","x":"50","fadetime":"3","id":396},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"50","xTo":"0","duration":"8","block":"false","id":397},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我们不可能战胜死亡，但我们能够......我们应该给生命以生活的尊严。","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我想......塔拉人应该，在夜晚有一簇温暖的火，在唱起歌谣时杯中有酒。","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"塔拉人应该，有一天不用再逃亡，不用与自己的亲人和爱人分离。","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我希望，塔拉人有自己平静生活的家园。","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我希望，这一路上我们告别的所有人，能够在那里重逢。","id":403},{"type":"dialog","id":404},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/49/Avg_bg_34_g2_reedmarshes.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":406},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"8","id":407},{"type":"image","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":408},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":409},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"wind","id":410},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"reed","id":411},{"type":"text","text":"风吹过芦苇，沙沙声中，她感到跳动的火焰带来的灼痛。","id":412},{"type":"text","text":"她知道，那是平实却遥远的梦想，此刻站在这里的人，或许谁都见不到那一天的到来。","id":413},{"type":"dialog","id":414},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":416},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"reed","id":417},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1.5","channel":"wind","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......深池的火会烧向这片土地。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"它......一定很残酷。千千万万的生命，都只能成为战火的燃料。","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"可是，就算到了那个时候，生命的重量，也绝不会减轻。","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......走吧，我们也在其中。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"对了，昨天我收到了家里来的信。","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"他们都过得还行，活着，也许我们打完仗回去，能看到他们生活得更好一点，哈哈。","id":428,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"莫兰，你又不说话了。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"抱歉，我只是在想，生活应该是什么样子？","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":432},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_victorianormal_loop.mp3","volume":"0","id":433,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":434},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":435},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":436},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"4","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......那么，你想唱唱歌吗？","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"唱吧，趁着难得的好日子，没有人追杀我们。","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_728_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":443},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":444},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":445},{"type":"text","text":"我在壁炉的火光旁安睡，梦见蜂蜜、甜酒与浓汤♪","id":446},{"type":"dialog","id":447},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":448},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"不过，苇草，要是我们和深池一起行动，你怎么办？","id":450,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_243.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"reed","fadetime":"3","id":451},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"wind","fadetime":"3","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不用担心。","id":454,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"既然我们想要实现的是同一个关于塔拉人的梦想，我和她就没有区别。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"到那一天，我会去见她。","id":456,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_1020_reed2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":457},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":458},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":459},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":460},{"type":"character","id":461},{"type":"charslot","id":462},{"type":"image","id":463}],"characters":["爱布拉娜","苇草","莫兰","塔拉流民","维多利亚军官","深池军官","受伤的塔拉人"]}